e.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Olivia-Rodrigo-Credit-Nick-Walker-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Olivia-Rodrigo-Credit-Nick-Walker-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Olivia-Rodrigo-Credit-Nick-Walker-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Olivia-Rodrigo-Credit-Nick-Walker-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="/artists/olivia-rodrigo">奥利维亚·罗德里戈 (Olivia Rodrigo)</a>宣布将于 2024 年举办<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/olivia-rodrigo-guts-album-review-vampire-3493907">“Guts”</a>世界巡演，以支持她的第二张同名专辑。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多：<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/olivia-rodrigo-guts-album-review-vampire-3493907">奥利维亚·罗德里戈 (Olivia Rodrigo) – 《胆量》评论：流行音乐的轰动确保了她作为一代天才的地位</a></strong></li></ul><p>这次为期 57 场的巡演将于 2024 年 2 月在加利福尼亚州棕榈泉拉开帷幕。从那里，罗德里戈将途径休斯顿、达拉斯、迈阿密、纳什维尔、芝加哥、底特律和多伦多等主要城市。</p><p>随后，她将于 2024 年 4 月在纽约市麦迪逊广场花园进行为期两晚的跑步比赛，然后飞往爱尔兰都柏林，在该市的 3Arena 进行比赛。这位流行歌手将在格拉斯哥和伯明翰进一步停留，然后在伦敦 O2 音乐厅演出两晚。</p><p> 2024 年 5 月和 6 月，罗德里戈将接管欧洲，并在比利时、丹麦、德国、意大利和西班牙停留。 For the final stretch of the tour, she will return to the States with shows in Philadelphia, Washington DC, Utah, and Colorado before wrapping up the tour in August 2024 with two nights at the Kia Forum in Inglewood, California. </p><figure id="attachment_3497479" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3497479" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3497479" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/GUTS-world-tour-poster.-Credit-PRESS.jpg" alt="'GUTS' world tour poster. Credit: PRESS" width="2000" height="2000" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/GUTS-world-tour-poster.-Credit-PRESS.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/GUTS-world-tour-poster.-Credit-PRESS-150x150.jpg 150w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/GUTS-world-tour-poster.-Credit-PRESS-400x400.jpg 400w, h