 said. “It was a combination of a bunch of people. It was a type, so it wasn&#39;t a diss on her. Someone else was more the personality of [Anna Faris&#39; character].”</p><p> <em>Her</em> is a sci-fi romance drama which follows Theodore Twombly (Joaquin Phoenix) as he develops a relationship with an AI female voice named Samantha (Scarlett Johansson). Rooney Mara plays Catherine, Theodore&#39;s childhood sweetheart who is pushing for a divorce from him.</p><p> Coppola&#39;s next film is biopic <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/film-reviews/priscilla-review-elvis-presley-sofia-coppola-3493033"><em>Priscilla</em></a> , based on the 1985 memoir <em>Elvis And Me</em> by Priscilla Presley. The film stars Cailee Spaeny and Jacob Elordi as Priscilla and <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/elvis-presley">Elvis Presley</a> respectively.</p><p> <em>Priscilla</em> is released in cinemas on November 3, 2023.</p><p> The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/sofia-coppola-still-cant-watch-ex-husband-spike-jonze-her-3497461">Sofia Coppola still can&#39;t watch ex-husband Spike Jonze&#39;s &#39;Her&#39;</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ;
